#. [scenario]: id=2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:30
msgid "Beginning of the Crusade"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:57
msgid ""
"After some preparation, the two brothers set out on their crusade. Shumsk "
"was the city closest to the border, taking it would mean gaining control "
"over the whole South of Krada. But the city fortress was well defended by a "
"large moat and high walls with guard towers, it also had a port which "
"allowed fast Krad's boats to quickly bring reinforcements."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:60
msgid ""
"This wasn't an easy task, but it was the matter of honour! Brothers, using "
"most of the gold from their treasury, hired siege engineers from Wesnoth. "
"Still the way to Shumsk didn't promise to be easy to deliver needed "
"equipment."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:63
msgid ""
"To provide a safe passage for their essential siege equipment, brothers "
"decided to use their vanguard to quickly take the border town. As they "
"expected, they found and hired a band of Steppe Ogres to assist in the "
"assault."
msgstr ""

#. [side]: id=ogre_ally, type=Ogre_Foreman
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:102
msgid "Chinggis"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:232
msgid "It is an honour to die in battle... argh..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=enemy_side{SIDE}
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:267
msgid "Defend the outpost!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=enemy_side{SIDE}
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:274
msgid "We're under attack!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=enemy_side{SIDE}
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:281
msgid "Look, there's an enemy army approaching! To arms!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Pan
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:303
msgid ""
"And so begins our crusade! This border town stands in the way to Krada. We "
"will capture it to allow our siege equipment a safe passage to Shumsk."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Brother
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:307
msgid "Scouts report that three outposts ahead keep watch over there."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Pan
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:311
msgid ""
"(quietly) <i>Good thing we took that slashing fellow. I propose we gather "
"our forces and wait a bit, let him strike first. His brutes will distract "
"the watchmen, then we attack.</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Brother
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:315
msgid "(quietly) <i>Indeed. Free cannon fodder is always nice.</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Pan
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:319
msgid "<i>It wasn't free, mind you! Anyway...</i> "
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Pan
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:323
msgid ""
"(To Chinggis) Hey! Let's start this! As we agreed, all loot you take here is "
"yours."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=ogre_ally
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:327
msgid "Come boys, let's show 'em how real ogres fight!"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:336
msgid "Kill the northern enemy leader"
msgstr ""

#. [note]
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:345
msgid ""
"You don't have to kill leaders near the outposts, your goal is to kill the "
"leader in the town"
msgstr ""

#. [note]
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:348
msgid ""
"Outpost leaders recieve gold and start recruiting when your or your ally's "
"units come closer. The first triggered outpost recieves the most gold"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:399
msgid "Argh... I failed to stop the invasion..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Brother
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:409
msgid ""
"With this town captured they can't seriously bother us. The way for our "
"siege machines to Shumsk is secured."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=ogre_ally
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:415
msgid "Shumsk? Ya crazy, city well prepare, you won't be able to show'em!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Pan
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:419
msgid ""
"It is our problem to handle. As we agreed, take everything that you looted "
"here. Also I wouldn't mind you pillaging all neighbour villages if you don't "
"feel like <i>showing'em</i>."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=ogre_ally
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:423
msgid "Gggrrr... good. You remember my word, we true ogres know."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Pan
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:429
msgid ""
"Meh, that madcap would've been useful to pillage all the neighbouring "
"villages, pity he died. Whatever."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Pan
#: scenarios/2_Beginning_of_the_Crusade.cfg:433
msgid "At least he was pretty decent cannon fodder."
msgstr ""

