#: scenarios/4_Time_to_Preach.cfg:95
msgid "Time to Preach"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: scenarios/4_Time_to_Preach.cfg:121
msgid ""
"Shumsk was captured. But to capture isn't the end of the day - one needs to "
"establish the rule in lands one conquered."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: scenarios/4_Time_to_Preach.cfg:124
msgid ""
"Meanwhile ogres' clerics were looking forward to preaching to the population "
"of the newly obtained lands. Brothers decided that it would be very "
"benefical to support their zeal: converting the population into ogres' faith "
"would entrench their rule, and at the same time brothers would receive the "
"respert of the clergy of the whole Ogres Kingdom."
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: scenarios/4_Time_to_Preach.cfg:561
msgid "Kill the enemy leader"
msgstr ""

